<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Welcome to StrokeWise Premium!</title>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body {
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      background: linear-gradient(160deg, #f8f4ef, #eef4f8);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }
    .card {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 40px 28px;
      max-width: 420px;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(30,58,95,0.1);
    }
    .emoji { font-size: 56px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    h1 { color: #1e3a5f; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    p { color: #5a6a7a; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .badge {
      background: rgba(42,127,138,0.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(42,127,138,0.3);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #2a7f8a;
      font-weight: 700;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2a7f8a, #1e3a5f);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 16px;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-family: Georgia, serif;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      width: 100%;
    }
    .note {
      margin-top: 16px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9aabb8;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="emoji">🎉</div>
    <h1>Welcome to StrokeWise Premium!</h1>
    <p>Your 7-day free trial has started. You now have full access to all premium brain training exercises, caregiver resources, and recovery tools.</p>
    <div class="badge">✓ Premium Active</div>
    <a href="https://strokewise-app.vercel.app" class="btn">
      Go to StrokeWise →
    </a>
    <p class="note">
      You won't be charged until your trial ends.<br/>
      Cancel anytime — no questions asked.
    </p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>